snippet.title: Necrobarista - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
UPDATE: Necrobarista launches July 22, 2020.

Wishlist us on Steam to be notified when the game comes out: https://store.steampowered.com/app/725270/Necrobarista/

In a magical Melbourne cafe, the dead return for one last night.

NECROBARISTA is an original visual novel combining a supernatural suspense story with a stylised cinematic presentation influenced by anime aesthetics.

https://twitter.com/route59games
http://www.necrobarista.com/
https://www.facebook.com/route59games/
